##### Block Grid
Block grids are designed to allow you to split a certain amount of content evenly between a grid layout. If you use the `small-block-grid` only, the grid will keep its spacing and configuration no matter the screen size. If you use `large-block-grid` only, the list items will stack on top of each other for small devices. If you use both of those classes combined, you can control the configuration and layout separately for each breakpoint.
{{/ markdown}}
